498
00:39:39.335 --> 00:39:41.128
Memento Mori.

499
00:39:41.713 --> 00:39:43.797
Reminders of mortality.

500
00:39:45.091 --> 00:39:46.884
It's all got to go.

501
00:39:48.845 --> 00:39:51.054
