collecting them.

502
00:39:51.556 --> 00:39:55.559
Every culture. every faith
and philosophy have their own.

503
00:39:56.728 --> 00:39:59.062
Some wrestling with death.

504
00:39:59.147 --> 00:40:00.606
Others dancing with it.

505
