509
00:40:13.995 --> 00:40:15.829
Like it found my grandson.

510
00:40:16.706 --> 00:40:18.248
Like it found me.

511
00:40:21.461 --> 00:40:23.295
Half a lifetime ago.

512
00:40:23.379 --> 00:40:26.089
