1083
01:26:15.253 --> 01:26:16.379
Ellie!

1084
01:26:16.797 --> 01:26:20.257
You're Chrysanthemum.

1085
01:26:21.718 --> 01:26:22.718
Ellie!

1086
01:26:28.350 --> 01:26:29.642
Ellie!

1087
01:26:32.229 --> 01:26:33.229
Ellie!

1088
01:27:01.091 --> 01:27:02.133
