those in need.

1094
01:27:20.777 --> 01:27:21.777
But you...

1095
01:27:22.612 --> 01:27:24.655
you're beyond redemption.

1096
01:27:25.741 --> 01:27:26.615
Whereas I...

1097
01:27:26.992 --> 01:27:29.201
