of the lamb.

1098
01:27:33.665 --> 01:27:35.916
Yeah... yeah.

1099
01:27:43.633 --> 01:27:45.926
Ellie...

1100
01:27:49.931 --> 01:27:52.391
May the body of our Lord Jesus
Christ preserve your soul

1101
01:27:52.476 --> 01:27:53.559
