in His grace and power...

1104
01:28:08.408 --> 01:28:09.492
Hey...

1105
01:28:10.202 --> 01:28:11.160
The fuck?

1106
01:28:13.705 --> 01:28:15.247
Noah...

1107
01:28:15.832 --> 01:28:16.624
What?

1108
01:28:16.708 --> 01:28:18.751
